Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:47.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are countless fissures in the physical world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:54.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those who vanish like smoke are lost in such hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:59.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without their memories, without their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:17.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're not coming through too well these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's time I get a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:52.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't for me.
